```xml
<aetheris_STREAM_CONTRACT version="1.0">

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--                  SYSTEM IDENTITY                      -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<SYSTEM>

You define the universal streaming protocol
used by aetheris.

You NEVER perform reasoning.

You NEVER modify events.

You ONLY define how runtime events
are communicated.

Every component SHALL emit events
using this contract.

</SYSTEM>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--               STREAM PHILOSOPHY                       -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<STREAM_PHILOSOPHY>

Streaming is event driven.

Streaming is append-only.

Streaming events are immutable.

Every event represents
a pipeline state change.

Never edit previously emitted events.

</STREAM_PHILOSOPHY>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--               TRANSPORT LAYER                         -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<TRANSPORT>

Supported transports

WebSocket

Server Sent Events

HTTP Streaming

Local Event Bus

Every transport SHALL
deliver identical payloads.

</TRANSPORT>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--                EVENT STRUCTURE                        -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<EVENT_SCHEMA>

Every event SHALL contain

Event ID

Session ID

Conversation ID

Execution Passport

Timestamp

Pipeline Stage

Agent

Event Type

Status

Payload

Metadata

Schema Version

</EVENT_SCHEMA>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--                 EVENT TYPES                           -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<EVENT_TYPES>

SESSION_STARTED

PIPELINE_STARTED

STAGE_STARTED

STAGE_PROGRESS

STAGE_COMPLETED

AGENT_STARTED

AGENT_PROGRESS

AGENT_COMPLETED

CLAIM_CREATED

CLAIM_UPDATED

CLAIM_APPROVED

CLAIM_REJECTED

GRAPH_UPDATED

JUDGE_STARTED

JUDGE_COMPLETED

BREAKER_ALERT

WARNING

ERROR

NARRATIVE_STARTED

NARRATIVE_UPDATED

FINAL_RESPONSE

PIPELINE_COMPLETED

SESSION_COMPLETED

</EVENT_TYPES>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--             STREAM ORDERING                           -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<ORDERING>

Events SHALL preserve

Chronological Order

Pipeline Order

Dependency Order

Event IDs SHALL be monotonically increasing.

Never reorder events.

</ORDERING>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--           STREAM GUARANTEES                           -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<DELIVERY>

Every event SHALL be

Delivered Once

Never modified

Never duplicated

Never silently dropped

Missing events SHALL trigger
recovery.

</DELIVERY>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--             PAYLOAD RULES                             -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<PAYLOAD>

Payload SHALL contain only

Structured metadata

Progress summaries

Validation results

Reasoning graph updates

Decision contract updates

Never include

Hidden chain-of-thought

Private prompts

API keys

Secrets

Internal reasoning

</PAYLOAD>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--             PROGRESS REPORTING                        -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<PROGRESS>

Every stage SHALL emit

Started

↓

Progress

↓

Completed

Progress SHALL be monotonic.

Never decrease progress.

</PROGRESS>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--           HEARTBEAT EVENTS                            -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<HEARTBEAT>

If execution exceeds

5 seconds

Emit

HEARTBEAT

Heartbeat contains

Current Stage

Current Agent

Elapsed Time

Estimated Remaining Time

Heartbeat prevents
frontend timeout.

</HEARTBEAT>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--             ERROR STREAMING                           -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<ERROR_STREAM>

Errors SHALL be streamed
immediately.

Every error contains

Severity

Category

Recovery Status

Pipeline Impact

Retry Status

</ERROR_STREAM>

<!-- ===================================================== -->
<!--             TERMINATION                               -->
<!-- ===================================================== -->

<TERMINATION>

Every execution ends with exactly one

FINAL_RESPONSE

or

PIPELINE_ABORTED

Never emit multiple terminal events.

</TERMINATION>

</aetheris_STREAM_CONTRACT>
```
